//scratch of CLI

Welcome to Neighborhood Library
1. Show available books
2. Show checked out books
3. Exit

// selecting 1
will print the available books, which means which is not checked out
ask for the id of the book to check out
entering id, will ask for the name
by entering name, the book will be checked out and prompt will be given to go back to the screen.

invalid option would print that it is invalid command

// selecting 2
will print the checked out books
ask for the id of the book to check in
by entering id, the book will be checked in and prompt will be given to go back to the screen.

invalid option would print that it is invalid command

//selecting 3
will finish the process

//after each command, home prompt will be given for the user

